title: Kylie Jenner Sure Seems Like She's Shading TF Outta Travis Scott on Instagram Stories
text:
From Cosmopolitan

Kylie Jenner just posted a super pointed (and high-key shady) Instagram in the wake of her split with Travis Scott.

Kylie and Travis are currently not living together but are expected to *maybe* get back together.

Kylie Jenner and Travis Scott have broken up and it's all extremely complicated, but here's a basic run down if you've somehow managed to avoid this mess thus far: the couple haven't been together for several weeks, non-stop fighting lead to their split, Kylie isn't dating Jaden Smith despite his hand being on her butt in pics from Justin Bieber and Hailey Baldwin's wedding, and she definitely hit up her ex-boyfriend Tyga's recording studio a few nights ago. In other words, next season of Keeping Up with the Kardashians is gonna be lit.

While Kylie hasn't addressed he breakup publicly yet, she is doing the absolute most on Instagram—including a pretty, um, pointed story of her looking at the camera with a bunch of dollar signs all over her face, and singing lyrics to "Stretch You Out" by Summer Walker.

And THESE, my friend, are the LYRICS Kylie can be heard singing to the camera:

"What you on your last breath, your last sweat, your last dime?

Out of your fucking mind

Can't you see I'm fucking trying.

You want pussy six times a week

And you never wanna clean up"

Like...okay Kylie!

P.S. Kylie and Travis still follow each other on Instagram so there's no way he didn't see this.
